## Pages

### Page 1 (index.html) - Landing Page
- Hero section with CTA
- Features grid
- Banner button for events

### Page 2 (page2.html) - Ticket Selection
- Quantity selectors for male/female tickets
- Validation (at least one ticket required)
- Warning modal before proceeding

### Page 3 (page3.html) - Payment
- Order summary
- Stripe Payment Element
- Terms and conditions checkbox
- Processing and success modals with QR code

## Features

- **Multi-language support**: English, Spanish, Portuguese (Brazil)
- **Responsive design**: Mobile-first, works on all devices
- **Accessible**: Keyboard navigation, screen reader friendly
- **Secure**: XSS prevention, URL validation, Stripe security
- **Fast**: System fonts, optimized CSS, lazy loading

## Configuration

Edit `public/js/config/index.js`:
```javascript
export const CONFIG = {
  BACKEND_URL: 'https://your-backend-url.com',
  STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY: 'pk_test_your_key_here',
  // ...
};
```

